com.stremebase.map

Class ListMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stremebase.base.StremeMap
      • com.stremebase.base.DynamicMap
        • com.stremebase.map.ListMap

  • public class ListMap
extends DynamicMap
    A map for associating a dynamic-sized array of values with a key. Supports stack operations push and pop, not modifications to middle of list. Removing from middle can be simulated by overwriting with DB.NULL.
